OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fmoving north during the day as Storm
OL,7,FDave arrives. The rain becoming heavy
OL,8,Fand persistent in the northwest later.
OL,9,FStrengthening winds for all with gales
OL,10,Fand severe gales developing,
OL,11,Fparticularly in the north and west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FVery windy with gales and
OL,14,Fperhaps severe gales across parts of
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, Scotland and
OL,16,Fnorthern England for a time. Outbreaks
OL,17,Fof rain, with snow over modest hills
OL,18,Facross Scotland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
