OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloud, rain and hill snow
OL,6,Facross the far northeast clearing, as
OL,7,Fwinds continue to ease. Sunny spells
OL,8,Fand blustery showers for many, but
OL,9,Fsouthern areas may to stay dry. Chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
